  "text": "REGD.NO D. L.-33004/99 The Gazette of India EXTRAORDINARY PART II—Section 3—Sub-section (ii) PUBLISHED BY AUTHORITY No. 704) NEW DELHI, TUESDAY, AUGUST6, 2002/SRAVANA 15, 1924 MINISTRY OF WATER RESOURCES (BM Section) NOTIFICATION New Delhi, the 6th August, 2002 S.O. 828{E).—In exercise of power conferred by sub-section (2) of section 1 of the Inter State Water Disputes (Amendment) Act, 2002 (14 of 2002), the Central Government hereby appoints the 6th day August, 2002 as the date on which the said Act shall come into force. [No.5/2/98-BM(Vol.-III)] M.K. SHARMA, Commissioner (Projects). 2461 GI/2002 Printed by the Manager, Govt, of India Press, Ring Road, Mayapuri, New Delhi-110064 and Published by the Controller of Publications, Delhi-110054. -- 1 of 2 -- -- 2 of 2 --",
